---
export const prerender = true;
import Legal from '../../layouts/Legal.astro';
---

<Legal 
  title="Privacy Policy" 
  description="How Passr handles and protects your data under GDPR and EU regulations.">
  
  <div class="legal-meta-bar">
    LAST UPDATED: APRIL 24, 2026
  </div>

  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy describes how Hisako Technologies GmbH ("Passr", "we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and discloses your personal data when you use our website at passr.eu, our platform, and our digital product passport services.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
  <p>
    The data controller responsible for your personal data under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is:
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Hisako Technologies GmbH</strong><br />
    Industrial Compliance Division<br />
    Berlin, Germany<br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@passr.eu">privacy@passr.eu</a>
  </p>

  <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
  <p>
    We collect and process data to provide our industrial-grade compliance services. The following table outlines the data types and our legal basis for processing:
  </p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Data Type</th>
        <th>Purpose</th>
        <th>Legal Basis</th>
        <th>Retention</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Account Data</td>
        <td>Service delivery (Name, Email, Brand)</td>
        <td>Contract (Art. 6.1.b)</td>
        <td>Account + 30 days</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Brand Data</td>
        <td>VAT, Logo, Verification status</td>
        <td>Contract (Art. 6.1.b)</td>
        <td>Account + 30 days</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Product Data</td>
        <td>SKUs, Material Composition, Certs</td>
        <td>Contract (Art. 6.1.b)</td>
        <td>Account + 30 days</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Passport Scans</td>
        <td>Anonymized analytics (Region, Device)</td>
        <td>Legitimate Int. (Art. 6.1.f)</td>
        <td>24 Months</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Billing Data</td>
        <td>Payment & Tax processing</td>
        <td>Legal (Art. 6.1.c)</td>
        <td>7 Years (Tax)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Waitlist Data</td>
        <td>Early access notifications</td>
        <td>Consent (Art. 6.1.a)</td>
        <td>Until unsubscribe</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

